FINAL PROJECT: FUTURAMA

Sasha Farhat
CSCI4229 Fall 2021

Many parts of this project was borrowed from previous assignments in this class. This include basic shapes such as cubes and cylinders and cone. I borrowed texture formatting from assignment 6. I borrowed lighting from homework 5. I borrowed perspective (first person), from my assignment 4. 

